"""
VitalLens vs Our rPPG Model — Full Cross-Dataset Benchmark
==========================================================
Evaluates two models on UBFC-rPPG, MCD-rPPG (held-out), and rPPG-10:
  1. VitalLens EfficientPhys (onnx, SCAMPS→UBFC LOSO fine-tuned)
  2. Our Phase 1 model (FactorizePhys+FSAM, SCAMPS-augmented adapted)

Both models are evaluated on IDENTICAL pre-processed clips (our existing caches)
to ensure a fair, controlled comparison.

Protocol: per-clip HR via FFT peak, averaged per subject for HR-level MAE.
No pipeline differences — same clips, same HR extraction, same outlier filter.

Expected input shapes:
  - Our model:   [1, 3, 161, 72, 72] float32 in [0,1]
  - VitalLens:   [1, 160, 3, 128, 128] float32 in [0,1]
                 (DiffNorm input: frame_t+1 - frame_t / (frame_t+1 + frame_t))
"""
